1
00:01:56,200 --> 00:02:00,933
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Hello blue skies and</i>
<i>sunshine! It's the moment</i>
<i>we've all been waiting for!</i>

2
00:02:00,966 --> 00:02:03,000
<i>(cont'd)</i>
<i>Summer break is</i>
<i>finally here!</i>

3
00:02:03,033 --> 00:02:06,633
(cont'd)
Wait, what's going on?!
Is someone trying to ruin
our vacation?

4
00:02:06,666 --> 00:02:09,533
<i>(cont'd)</i>
<i>And look! They're robbing</i>
<i>an innocent girl of her</i>
<i>future!</i>

5
00:02:09,566 --> 00:02:11,666
<i>(cont'd)</i>
<i>That's just</i>
<i>unforgivable!</i>

6
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:16,766
<i>I am Sailor Moon!</i>
And in the name of the
moon! I'll punish you!

7
00:02:18,566 --> 00:02:23,533
<i>Hi! I'm Usagi Tsukino!</i>
<i>It may not look it, but</i>
<i>I'm actually a superhero!</i>

8
00:02:23,566 --> 00:02:25,966
<i>I use a special brooch</i>
<i>to transform and fight</i>
<i>evil!</i>

9
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:30,400
<i>You know me as, the</i>
<i>Pretty Guardian who fights</i>
<i>for love and for justice!</i>

10
00:02:30,433 --> 00:02:32,400
<i>I am Sailor Moon!</i>

11
00:02:32,433 --> 00:02:36,800
<i>I'm friends with the</i>
<i>kindhearted genius,</i>
<i>Ami Mizuno, who's</i>
<i>Sailor Mercury!</i>

12
00:02:36,833 --> 00:02:39,933
<i>And Rei Hino, the</i>
<i>hotheaded psychic, who's</i>
<i>Sailor Mars!</i>

13
00:02:39,966 --> 00:02:43,000
<i>Both of them seem to</i>
<i>have it a little more</i>
<i>together than I do!</i>

14
00:02:43,033 --> 00:02:47,766
<i>But, oh well. Guess</i>
<i>I just gotta do my</i>
<i>best!</i>
<i>(Giggles)</i>

15
00:02:51,866 --> 00:02:57,700
"The Summer, The Beach,
Youth, And Ghosts."

16
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:07,500
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Ah!</i>

17
00:03:07,533 --> 00:03:10,266
We made it!
We're finally here!

18
00:03:15,866 --> 00:03:16,933
(All)
Wow!

19
00:03:16,966 --> 00:03:18,433
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Look at the beach!</i>

20
00:03:18,466 --> 00:03:20,533
<i>(Ami)</i>
<i>The sea breeze is</i>
<i>so refreshing!</i>

21
00:03:20,566 --> 00:03:23,333
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>Yeah, this place is</i>
<i>really nice!</i>

22
00:03:23,366 --> 00:03:25,966
It's too bad we
couldn't have brought
Naru along with us!

23
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,666
We are not here to have
fun, Usagi!

24
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:32,833
Remember, we're here
for a Sailor Guardian
summer training camp!
(Egh!)

25
00:03:32,866 --> 00:03:35,566
Way to ruin the
moment, Luna!

26
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,833
Wow!

27
00:03:36,866 --> 00:03:38,600
(Ami)
How far is the pension
house we're staying
at?

28
00:03:38,633 --> 00:03:41,300
(Rei)
It's supposed to be
pretty close by.

29
00:03:41,333 --> 00:03:45,333
So Rei, I'm expecting
this hotel to be a
really swanky resort!

30
00:03:45,366 --> 00:03:46,400
Well, I think it is.

31
00:03:46,433 --> 00:03:48,133
Really?!

32
00:03:48,166 --> 00:03:52,466
It says here, "Blue
seas surround you as
yachts go gliding by!
From our luxurious

33
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:56,933
(cont'd)
pension house <i>you can view</i>
<i>a beautiful sunset over our</i>
<i>gleaming private beach!</i>

34
00:03:56,966 --> 00:03:59,633
Our own private beach!

35
00:04:00,933 --> 00:04:07,766
(Crowd Talking)

36
00:04:09,533 --> 00:04:12,666
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Motoki, it's you!</i>
<i>(Giggles)</i>

37
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:14,266
Huh?

38
00:04:15,966 --> 00:04:19,233
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Tuxedo Mask!</i>

39
00:04:19,866 --> 00:04:22,566
Ah!! I can't wait!

40
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:28,500
This is it! This is
what I'm talking about!
Being young, at the beach
during summer break!

41
00:04:28,533 --> 00:04:31,766
Huh?
Eh? Gah!
Hey, wait for me!

42
00:04:34,866 --> 00:04:40,166
(Usagi Whining)
Are we there yet?
We're lost, aren't we?

43
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:43,400
That's because you
said it was definitely
this way!

44
00:04:43,433 --> 00:04:48,766
Ugh! No, we're lost
because you didn't plan
ahead well enough!
Dummy!

45
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:50,466
What did you call
me?!

46
00:04:50,500 --> 00:04:53,800
(Thunder Rolling)

47
00:04:53,833 --> 00:04:54,966
Ahh!

48
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:57,766
Thunder! Looks like
it's really gonna
pour on us!

49
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,600
We better get going!

50
00:04:59,633 --> 00:05:00,533
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>Right!</i>

51
00:05:00,566 --> 00:05:02,566
Ahh!

52
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,766
I'm really scared of
thunder!

53
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:11,300
Ahh!

54
00:05:11,533 --> 00:05:12,866
<i>(Luna)</i>
<i>Usagi!</i>

55
00:05:12,900 --> 00:05:13,866
(Ami)
What's wrong?!

56
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:15,300
Who's there?!

57
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:15,933
Oh!

58
00:05:15,966 --> 00:05:17,633
Uh! Sorry I scared
you!

59
00:05:17,666 --> 00:05:19,233
(All)
Huh?

60
00:05:19,266 --> 00:05:20,400
(All)
Awe!

61
00:05:20,433 --> 00:05:21,833
Now it's raining!

62
00:05:21,866 --> 00:05:23,866
Uh, please, follow
me!

63
00:05:25,366 --> 00:05:26,666
C'mon! Let's go!

64
00:05:26,700 --> 00:05:28,333
(Usagi)
Okay...

65
00:05:30,566 --> 00:05:34,566
(Lightning Strike)

66
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:37,866
(Usagi)
Ahh!
Make it stop!

67
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:41,500
I can't take it
anymore! I wanna
go home now!

68
00:05:47,300 --> 00:05:49,833
Uh- That looks
creepy.

69
00:05:53,233 --> 00:05:56,200
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>This is the place!</i>
<i>We've made it to the</i>
<i>pension.</i>

70
00:05:56,233 --> 00:05:58,200
(Usagi)
What?! We're staying
here?!

71
00:05:58,233 --> 00:05:59,400
(Rei)
What's your problem?

72
00:05:59,433 --> 00:06:01,566
This place looks
haunted.

73
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,766
Thank you, you
really helped us!

74
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,700
(Giggles)
We're absolutely
soaked.

75
00:06:05,733 --> 00:06:06,766
Are your flowers okay?

76
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,166
Oh. yes!

77
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,233
That's good!

78
00:06:14,233 --> 00:06:15,400
(Cowering)

79
00:06:20,833 --> 00:06:22,366
Welcome!

80
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,600
Welcome!

81
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:25,600
Welcome!

82
00:06:25,633 --> 00:06:27,566
Ah!

83
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,066
(Sakiko)
Hi.

84
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:31,200
(All Three)
Welcome back, Miss.

85
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:35,566
So, do you three ladies
have a reservation?

86
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,400
Yes, we do!
I'm Rei Hino, from
Tokyo.

87
00:06:38,433 --> 00:06:41,166
We've been expecting
your arrival!

88
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,133
Eee-eee!

89
00:06:43,166 --> 00:06:44,300
(All Three)
Come in!

90
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:45,266
Thanks.

91
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:47,033
(Ami)
Thank you for having
us.
Oh!

92
00:06:47,066 --> 00:06:48,533
N-nice to meet you!

93
00:06:48,566 --> 00:06:52,166
How long are you going
to keep making a scene
here?! It's embarrassing!

94
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,366
But, I, uh...

95
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:55,100
<i>(Father)</i>
<i>Sakiko!</i>

96
00:06:56,566 --> 00:06:58,033
Ahh!

97
00:06:58,066 --> 00:06:59,500
Calm down already!

98
00:06:59,533 --> 00:07:00,400
Huh?

99
00:07:00,433 --> 00:07:04,100
So just where were
you?! Get over here!

100
00:07:04,133 --> 00:07:06,433
Uh, yes father.
Right away!

101
00:07:08,766 --> 00:07:11,200
(Thunder)

102
00:07:12,666 --> 00:07:16,033
Aw, I'm hungry.
And so exhausted!

103
00:07:16,066 --> 00:07:18,066
(Luna)
Guess all that
screaming wore you
out.

104
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,300
Hey! You were
scared too!

105
00:07:19,333 --> 00:07:20,800
Uh..

106
00:07:20,833 --> 00:07:23,300
Seriously Luna, don't
you think the hotel
staff looked kinda
weird?

107
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:27,500
I mean, what if this
place really is haunted?
Maybe we should leave!

108
00:07:27,533 --> 00:07:28,366
Ah!

109
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,233
Uh, yes?

110
00:07:30,266 --> 00:07:32,300
Hello!

111
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:36,233
AHH!

112
00:07:36,266 --> 00:07:37,100
What's wrong?

113
00:07:37,133 --> 00:07:38,700
L-look behind you!

114
00:07:38,733 --> 00:07:39,566
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>Huh?</i>

115
00:07:42,266 --> 00:07:44,666
Ah, there! It came on!

116
00:07:44,700 --> 00:07:48,400
Sorry for bothering
you. It's time for
dinner now!

117
00:07:48,433 --> 00:07:49,366
Jeez!

118
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,666
Usagi!

119
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:54,700
But I swear! She
popped in here out of
nowhere.

120
00:07:54,733 --> 00:07:56,133
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>Now you're gonna</i>
<i>get it!</i>

121
00:07:56,166 --> 00:07:58,000
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>No! Ami, help!</i>

122
00:07:58,033 --> 00:08:00,066
(Ami)
Not this time, Usagi!
You're on your own!

123
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:02,100
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>But Ami!</i>
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>No buts for you, bunhead!</i>

124
00:08:02,133 --> 00:08:03,266
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Hey, watch it!</i>

125
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:05,300
<i>(Father)</i>
<i>What a bunch of</i>
<i>noisy girls!</i>

126
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:06,933
<i>(Sakiko)</i>
<i>But they seemed like</i>
<i>very nice people.</i>

127
00:08:06,966 --> 00:08:12,233
Sakiko! Don't you go
getting involved with
such foolish girls?
Understand?!

128
00:08:12,266 --> 00:08:16,233
Yes, I won't, Father.

129
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:21,200
(Everybody Eating)

130
00:08:21,233 --> 00:08:23,400
Om!

131
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:28,433
Om!
Hm?

132
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:34,300
<i>(Cook)</i>
<i>So, would you like</i>
<i>seconds?</i>

133
00:08:34,333 --> 00:08:39,200
Ahh!
No thanks, I'm already
full!
(Nervously Laughing)

134
00:08:39,233 --> 00:08:40,400
<i>(Cook)</i>
<i>Okay...</i>

135
00:08:40,433 --> 00:08:41,633
(Gasps)

136
00:08:41,666 --> 00:08:43,700
Did you save some
room for dessert?

137
00:08:43,733 --> 00:08:45,300
No, I didn't,
but thanks!

138
00:08:45,333 --> 00:08:49,466
You stupid dummy!
What the heck made
you decide to pick this
place anyway?!

139
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:52,400
Duh, isn't it
obvious? It was
cheap.

140
00:08:52,433 --> 00:08:54,266
Agh!

141
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:58,300
Even so, the food here
is tasty and I really
like the funny costumes
that they're wearing.

142
00:08:58,333 --> 00:08:58,866
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>You do?!</i>

143
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:00,133
Nice to hear
that.

144
00:09:00,166 --> 00:09:03,333
That's actually one
of the selling points
of this pension.

145
00:09:03,366 --> 00:09:04,666
<i>(Ghostly Moans)</i>
(Usagi)
What now?!

146
00:09:04,700 --> 00:09:06,366
There it goes,
again!

147
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:09,066
That wailing! It's
sounds so scary!

148
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:11,000
(Rei)
Must be the owner
crying.

149
00:09:11,033 --> 00:09:13,233
No, that isn't me!

150
00:09:13,266 --> 00:09:17,366
(Usagi)
Ah! Why do you keep
popping in out of
nowhere!

151
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,966
Hnh! Hey!

152
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,133
<i>Ehh-Ehh!</i>

153
00:09:28,366 --> 00:09:30,300
Did you all see that?!

154
00:09:30,333 --> 00:09:33,166
(Owner)
We-We didn't see
anything!

155
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:37,866
Hear that Luna, we
must've been imagining
things!
(Nervous Laughing)

156
00:09:37,900 --> 00:09:39,333
Do you think it
was a monster?

157
00:09:39,366 --> 00:09:41,433
No, I'm not sensing
that there's one
here.

158
00:09:41,466 --> 00:09:44,966
However, I did sense
some kind of incredible
power.

159
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,466
Uh!

160
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:48,533
(Teeth chattering)

161
00:09:50,100 --> 00:09:56,933
<i>(Father)</i>
<i>Good girl. That's a</i>
<i>good girl. You're a</i>
<i>very good girl.</i>

162
00:09:56,966 --> 00:10:00,500
<i>(cont'd)</i>
<i>Now sleep, go to</i>
<i>sleep.</i>

163
00:10:00,533 --> 00:10:04,466
That's right.
Good girl.

164
00:10:04,500 --> 00:10:10,300
<i>(Father)</i>
<i>Your eyes are heavy.</i>
<i>Now, sleep.</i>

165
00:10:11,466 --> 00:10:17,200
Yes, listen to my
voice. You will now
slowly open your eyes.

166
00:10:17,233 --> 00:10:22,000
<i>(cont'd)</i>
<i>Gradually, very</i>
<i>slowly.</i>

167
00:10:22,033 --> 00:10:25,066
(Deep Laughter)

168
00:10:30,900 --> 00:10:34,133
<i>Sailor Moon!</i>

169
00:10:44,474 --> 00:10:47,507
<i>Sailor Moon!</i>

170
00:10:49,607 --> 00:10:51,574
Yippee!

171
00:10:52,807 --> 00:10:55,341
Check out those
great waves!

172
00:10:56,541 --> 00:10:57,907
Hmm!

173
00:10:57,941 --> 00:11:03,407
(Giggling)
Yay!
This feels great!

174
00:11:03,441 --> 00:11:05,874
(Rei)
It's like that storm
never happened!

175
00:11:05,907 --> 00:11:07,641
I know, this
weather's great!

176
00:11:07,674 --> 00:11:09,541
But something's
missing...

177
00:11:09,574 --> 00:11:12,007
I know, you're
right.

178
00:11:12,041 --> 00:11:15,041
<i>(Rei)</i>
<i>Well, this beach</i>
<i>certainly is private,</i>
<i>right?</i>

179
00:11:15,074 --> 00:11:19,007
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Yeah, so private</i>
<i>there's no one else</i>
<i>here but us.</i>

180
00:11:19,041 --> 00:11:24,341
Ships way offshore.
A flock of seagulls.
(Sigh)
Where are all the

181
00:11:24,374 --> 00:11:28,607
yachts that glide
by?! And all the hot
boys?!
(Whines)

182
00:11:28,641 --> 00:11:32,674
I hate this beach,
you hear me! I really
hate this beach!

183
00:11:32,707 --> 00:11:34,907
So who wants to
play ball?!

184
00:11:34,941 --> 00:11:37,474
(Groans)
Can I bury her in
the sand?

185
00:11:37,507 --> 00:11:42,407
Wait! we never did
see that girl Sakiko
come out of her room
this morning.

186
00:11:42,441 --> 00:11:46,741
Hey, you're right.
Wait! Hold on, Ami!
Did you bring some of
your textbooks here

187
00:11:46,774 --> 00:11:47,507
with you?!

188
00:11:47,541 --> 00:11:47,807
(Ami)
Mm-Hmm!

189
00:11:47,841 --> 00:11:49,541
Aghh!

190
00:11:49,574 --> 00:11:54,607
Hmph! Listen, Ami!
Youth is a precious
thing. You only get to
experience it once!

191
00:11:54,641 --> 00:11:58,007
I know studying's
important, but I think
it's just as important
to have fun and make

192
00:11:58,041 --> 00:12:00,307
some memories while
we're on this great
vacation!

193
00:12:00,341 --> 00:12:01,441
But, I like
books.

194
00:12:01,474 --> 00:12:05,474
Uh, Usagi said
something that makes
sense for once!

195
00:12:05,507 --> 00:12:09,241
(Giggles)
Okay, you win!
Come on, let's go
have some fun!

196
00:12:09,274 --> 00:12:10,907
Ha! Now that's
the spirit!

197
00:12:10,941 --> 00:12:12,407
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Here goes!</i>

198
00:12:12,441 --> 00:12:14,841
(Laughing)

199
00:12:14,874 --> 00:12:16,541
Ha!
Got it!

200
00:12:16,574 --> 00:12:17,574
Catch!

201
00:12:17,607 --> 00:12:18,974
Agh!

202
00:12:19,007 --> 00:12:20,941
(Gasps)
Catch!

203
00:12:20,974 --> 00:12:22,807
Agh!

204
00:12:22,841 --> 00:12:24,874
Hey! Stop picking
on me!

205
00:12:24,907 --> 00:12:27,241
(Giggling)

206
00:12:27,774 --> 00:12:30,741
<i>(Girls Playing)</i>
<i>I'll get you both!</i>
<i>You too, Luna!</i>

207
00:12:30,774 --> 00:12:34,441
(Girls Laughing)

208
00:12:34,474 --> 00:12:36,974
Ah-ooo!

209
00:12:37,007 --> 00:12:41,274
Oo-oo!
Ah-ooo!

210
00:12:41,307 --> 00:12:44,974
Aw! Nighttime's
here again.
I'm scared!

211
00:12:45,007 --> 00:12:48,907
<i>(Usagi)</i>
<i>Luna? You still there?</i>
<i>Luna!</i>

212
00:12:48,941 --> 00:12:51,407
For the tenth time!
Yes, I'm right here!

213
00:12:51,441 --> 00:12:54,441
But I'm really
super scared!

214
00:12:54,474 --> 00:12:57,841
Evil spirits, be
exorcised!

215
00:12:57,874 --> 00:13:00,374
This should keep us
safe while were
having our dinner.

216
00:13:00,407 --> 00:13:03,341
But, I'm pretty sure
that thing wasn't
a ghost.

217
00:13:03,374 --> 00:13:06,374
It felt like it
was real and really
powerful.

218
00:13:06,407 --> 00:13:08,774
<i>(Cook)</i>
